{
  "video_id": "dQijrruP9c4",
  "title": "Joan Halifax: Compassion and the true meaning of empathy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "I want to address the issue of compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "Compassion has many faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "Some of them are fierce; some of them are wrathful;"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "some of them are tender; some of them are wise."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "A line that the Dalai Lama once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "he said, \"Love and compassion are necessities."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "They are not luxuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "Without them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "humanity cannot survive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "And I would suggest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "it is not only humanity that won&#39;t survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "but it is all species on the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;ve heard today."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "It is the big cats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the plankton."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "Two weeks ago, I was in Bangalore in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "I was so privileged"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "to be able to teach in a hospice"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "on the outskirts of Bangalore."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "And early in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "I went into the ward."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "In that hospice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "there were 31 men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "who were actively dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "And I walked up to the bedside"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "of an old woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "who was breathing very rapidly, fragile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "obviously in the latter phase"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "of active dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "I looked into her face."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "I looked into the face"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "of her son sitting next to her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "and his face was just riven"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "with grief and confusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "And I remembered"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "a line from the Mahabharata,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "the great Indian epic:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "\"What is the most wondrous thing in the world, Yudhisthira?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "And Yudhisthira replied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "\"The most wondrous thing in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "is that all around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "people can be dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "it can happen to us.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "I looked up."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "Tending those 31 dying people"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "were young women"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "from villages around Bangalore."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "I looked into the face of one of these women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "and I saw in her face"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "the strength that arises"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "when natural compassion is really present."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "I watched her hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "as she bathed an old man."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "My gaze went to another young woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "as she wiped the face"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "of another dying person."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "And it reminded me"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "of something that I had just been present for."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "Every year or so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "I have the privilege of taking clinicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "into the Himalayas and the Tibetan Plateau."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "And we run clinics"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "in these very remote regions"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "where there&#39;s no medical care whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "And on the first day at Simikot in Humla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "far west of Nepal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "the most impoverished region of Nepal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "an old man came in"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "clutching a bundle of rags."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "And he walked in, and somebody said something to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "we realized he was deaf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "and we looked into the rags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "and there was this pair of eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "The rags were unwrapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "from a little girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "whose body was massively burned."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "Again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "the eyes and hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "of Avalokiteshvara."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 230260.0,
      "text": "It was the young women, the health aids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "who cleaned the wounds of this baby"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "and dressed the wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "I know those hands and eyes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "they touched me as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "They touched me at that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "They have touched me throughout my 68 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "They touched me when I was four"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "and I lost my eyesight"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "and was partially paralyzed."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "And my family brought in"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "a woman whose mother had been a slave"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "to take care of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "And that woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "did not have sentimental compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "She had phenomenal strength."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "And it was really her strength, I believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "that became the kind of mudra and imprimatur"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "that has been a guiding light in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "So we can ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "What is compassion comprised of?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "And there are various facets."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s referential and non-referential compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "But first, compassion is comprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "of that capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "to see clearly"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "into the nature of suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "It is that ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "to really stand strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "and to recognize also"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m not separate from this suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "But that is not enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "because compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "which activates the motor cortex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "means that we aspire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "we actually aspire to transform suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "And if we&#39;re so blessed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "we engage in activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "that transform suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "But compassion has another component,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "and that component is really essential."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "That component"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "is that we cannot be attached to outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "Now I worked with dying people"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "for over 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "I had the privilege of working on death row"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "in a maximum security [prison] for six years."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "And I realized so clearly"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "in bringing my own life experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "from working with dying people"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "and training caregivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "that any attachment to outcome"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "would distort deeply"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "my own capacity to be fully present"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "to the whole catastrophe."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "And when I worked in the prison system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 365260.0,
      "text": "it was so clear to me, this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 365260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "that many of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 372260.0,
      "text": "and almost all of the men that I worked with on death row,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "the seeds of their own compassion had never been watered."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "That compassion is actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "an inherent human quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "It is there within every human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "But the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 389260.0,
      "text": "for compassion to be activated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 389260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "to be aroused,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "are particular conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "I had that condition, to a certain extent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "from my own childhood illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "Eve Ensler, whom you&#39;ll hear later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "has had that condition activated"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "amazingly in her"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "through the various waters of suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "that she has been through."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "And what is fascinating"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "is that compassion has enemies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "and those enemies are things like pity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 425260.0,
      "text": "moral outrage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 425260.0,
      "end_time": 427260.0,
      "text": "fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "And you know, we have a society, a world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "that is paralyzed by fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "And in that paralysis, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "our capacity for compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "is also paralyzed."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "The very word terror"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "is global."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 443260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "The very feeling of terror is global."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "So our work, in a certain way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "is to address this imago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "this kind of archetype"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "that has pervaded the psyche"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "of our entire globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "Now we know from neuroscience"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "that compassion has"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "some very extraordinary qualities."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 465260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "For example:"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "A person who is cultivating compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "when they are in the presence of suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "they feel that suffering a lot more"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 478260.0,
      "text": "than many other people do."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 480260.0,
      "text": "However,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 480260.0,
      "end_time": 483260.0,
      "text": "they return to baseline a lot sooner."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 483260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "This is called resilience."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 488260.0,
      "text": "Many of us think that compassion drains us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 488260.0,
      "end_time": 490260.0,
      "text": "but I promise you"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 490260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "it is something that truly enlivens us."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "Another thing about compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "is that it really enhances what&#39;s called neural integration."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "It hooks up all parts of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 504260.0,
      "text": "Another, which has been discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 506260.0,
      "text": "by various researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "at Emory and at Davis and so on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "is that compassion enhances our immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "Hey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 518260.0,
      "text": "we live in a very noxious world."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "Most of us are shrinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 525260.0,
      "text": "in the face of psycho-social and physical poisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 525260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "of the toxins of our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "But compassion, the generation of compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 533260.0,
      "text": "actually mobilizes"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 533260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "our immunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "You know, if compassion is so good for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 539260.0,
      "end_time": 541260.0,
      "text": "I have a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t we train our children"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "in compassion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "If compassion is so good for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "why don&#39;t we train our health care providers in compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "so that they can do what they&#39;re supposed to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 566260.0,
      "text": "which is to really transform suffering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 566260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "And if compassion is so good for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 573260.0,
      "text": "why don&#39;t we vote on compassion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 573260.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "Why don&#39;t we vote for people in our government"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 577260.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "based on compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 579260.0,
      "end_time": 581260.0,
      "text": "so that we can have"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 581260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "a more caring world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 586260.0,
      "text": "In Buddhism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "we say, \"it takes a strong back and a soft front.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 592260.0,
      "text": "It takes tremendous strength of the back"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 592260.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "to uphold yourself in the midst of conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 595260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "And that is the mental quality of equanimity."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 598260.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "But it also takes a soft front --"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "the capacity to really be open to the world as it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "to have an undefended heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "And the archetype of this in Buddhism"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 611260.0,
      "text": "is Avalokiteshvara, Kuan-Yin."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 611260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a female archetype:"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "she who perceives"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "the cries of suffering in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 623260.0,
      "end_time": 627260.0,
      "text": "She stands with 10,000 arms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 627260.0,
      "end_time": 629260.0,
      "text": "and in every hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 629260.0,
      "end_time": 632260.0,
      "text": "there is an instrument of liberation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 632260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "and in the palm of every hand, there are eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 638260.0,
      "text": "and these are the eyes of wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 641260.0,
      "text": "I say that, for thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 643260.0,
      "text": "women have lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 643260.0,
      "end_time": 647260.0,
      "text": "exemplified, met in intimacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 650260.0,
      "text": "the archetype of Avalokitesvara,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "of Kuan-Yin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 654260.0,
      "text": "she who perceives"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 654260.0,
      "end_time": 656260.0,
      "text": "the cries of suffering in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "Women have manifested for thousands of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "the strength arising from compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 667260.0,
      "text": "in an unfiltered, unmediated way"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 667260.0,
      "end_time": 669260.0,
      "text": "in perceiving suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 669260.0,
      "end_time": 671260.0,
      "text": "as it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 673260.0,
      "end_time": 676260.0,
      "text": "They have infused societies with kindness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 676260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "and we have really felt that"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 680260.0,
      "text": "as woman after woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 680260.0,
      "end_time": 682260.0,
      "text": "has stood on this stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 682260.0,
      "end_time": 685260.0,
      "text": "in the past day and a half."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 685260.0,
      "end_time": 687260.0,
      "text": "And they have actualized compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 687260.0,
      "end_time": 689260.0,
      "text": "through direct action."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 689260.0,
      "end_time": 691260.0,
      "text": "Jody Williams called it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 691260.0,
      "end_time": 693260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s good to meditate."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 693260.0,
      "end_time": 696260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sorry, you&#39;ve got to do a little bit of that, Jody."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 696260.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "Step back, give your mother a break, okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 699260.0,
      "end_time": 701260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 701260.0,
      "end_time": 703260.0,
      "text": "But the other side of the equation"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 703260.0,
      "end_time": 705260.0,
      "text": "is you&#39;ve got to come out of your cave."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 705260.0,
      "end_time": 707260.0,
      "text": "You have to come into the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 707260.0,
      "end_time": 709260.0,
      "text": "like Asanga did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 709260.0,
      "end_time": 712260.0,
      "text": "who was looking to realize Maitreya Buddha"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 712260.0,
      "end_time": 715260.0,
      "text": "after 12 years sitting in the cave."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 715260.0,
      "end_time": 717260.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I&#39;m out of here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 717260.0,
      "end_time": 719260.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s going down the path."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 719260.0,
      "end_time": 721260.0,
      "text": "He sees something in the path."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 721260.0,
      "end_time": 724260.0,
      "text": "He looks, it&#39;s a dog, he drops to his knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 724260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "He sees that the dog has this big wound on its leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 728260.0,
      "end_time": 731260.0,
      "text": "The wound is just filled with maggots."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 731260.0,
      "end_time": 734260.0,
      "text": "He puts out his tongue"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 734260.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "in order to remove the maggots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 736260.0,
      "end_time": 739260.0,
      "text": "so as not to harm them."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 741260.0,
      "text": "And at that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 741260.0,
      "end_time": 743260.0,
      "text": "the dog transformed"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 743260.0,
      "end_time": 746260.0,
      "text": "into the Buddha of love and kindness."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 747260.0,
      "end_time": 749260.0,
      "text": "I believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 749260.0,
      "end_time": 751260.0,
      "text": "that women and girls today"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 751260.0,
      "end_time": 755260.0,
      "text": "have to partner in a powerful way with men --"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 755260.0,
      "end_time": 757260.0,
      "text": "with their fathers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 757260.0,
      "end_time": 760260.0,
      "text": "with their sons, with their brothers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 760260.0,
      "end_time": 762260.0,
      "text": "with the plumbers, the road builders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 762260.0,
      "end_time": 765260.0,
      "text": "the caregivers, the doctors, the lawyers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 765260.0,
      "end_time": 767260.0,
      "text": "with our president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 767260.0,
      "end_time": 769260.0,
      "text": "and with all beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 769260.0,
      "end_time": 771260.0,
      "text": "The women in this room"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 771260.0,
      "end_time": 774260.0,
      "text": "are lotuses in a sea of fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 774260.0,
      "end_time": 776260.0,
      "text": "May we actualize that capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 776260.0,
      "end_time": 778260.0,
      "text": "for women everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 778260.0,
      "end_time": 780260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 780260.0,
      "end_time": 792260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}